commitResults.messageBody:
Cosmetic changes are made to achieve the proposed UI. This includes:
- rearranging components under `MainWindow.fxml`
- changing the colour scheme
- spacing and font weight changes for visual hierarchy

To support our features proposed, containers are nested under as
> VBox (container to allow free resizing)
>> TabPane (supports different tabs)
>>> StackPane (contains list of contacts)

`Orders` and `Suppliers` currently has placeholder texts only.

Updated package name from seedu.address to trackr

Removed extra newlines in .gitignore

Closes #79 
Updated help text to new repo user guide
Updates project title for PPP of arkarsg and liumc-sg to reflect Trackr instead of AddressBook Level 3
This reverts commit 586032e36f148d06680f47e2bb9a1ec6a09367ad.
This reverts commit 241599401163b5bf039ce7bd33c82b55efe4cc97.

Key changes are made through `DarkTheme.css`:
- Colour scheme updated to reflect proposed UI design
- Resizes components for hierarchy
- Resizes Text for heirarchy

Following the UI proposed, tabs for different views are created. Contacts from AB3 is still used as sample data for `Home` page.
To allow resizing and extendability of the UI components, TabPane is contained by VBox.
This is because it is a known issue that font weights are not compatible on OSX. For equal experience of all users across all devices, this cosmetic issue will be removed.
